ShopList App

The ShopList App is designed to help users manage a list of shops. With a simple and intuitive interface, users can easily create, read, update, and delete shop details.

Model

The shop should have the following attributes:
name
opening date
whether it delivers to home or not


Features

1. User Authentication
Sign Up: New users can create an account using their email and password.
Login: Existing users can log in to access their list of shops.
Logout: Users can log out to ensure their data remains secure.
2. Shop Management
2.1. Create Shop

Users can add a new shop to their list by providing the following details:
Shop Name
Shop Address
Contact Number
Shop Type (e.g., Grocery, Electronics, Clothing, etc.)
Additional Notes or Description
2.2. Read Shop Details

Users can view a list of all the shops they've added.
Clicking on a shop name will display detailed information about that shop.
2.3. Update Shop Details

Users can edit any information related to a shop.
Changes are saved in real-time and can be viewed immediately.
2.4. Delete Shop

Users can remove a shop from their list.
A confirmation prompt ensures that shops are not deleted accidentally.
3. Search and Filter
Users can search for a specific shop by name.
Filter options allow users to view shops based on type or other criteria.
4. Responsive Design
The app is designed to be fully responsive, ensuring a seamless experience on both desktop and mobile devices.